{"tid":1896531,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[唔出聲冇人話你啞]中共五毛攻擊緊泛民，泛民就係到玩自爆","createTime":"2020-02-25T07:40:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-25T08:49:58.000Z","uid":107297,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"95d622871d2a4b4fa3e91bf8e992daf969c0f3f2","tid":1896531,"uid":107297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T07:40:09.000Z","msg":"首先，果D咩解散功能組別定奪取功能組別叫人投白票唔投票嘅9成五毛<br />\n票就一定要投<br />\n但係泛民可唔可以唔好玩自爆，比黑材料D五毛呢？<br />\n果300億如果泛民如果驚投反對會比對家抹黑，係咪可以離場抗議呢？還掂泛民都唔夠票反對（好似係，唔清楚）<br />\n果D滯留湖北港人，泛民完全可以唔出聲，唔出聲冇人話你啞<br />\n五毛已經攻擊緊你地，你地自己玩自爆<br />\n唔好唔記得，泛民冇我地呢D本土支持者投票個話，唔好話奪取功能組別，隨時直選都輸"},{"pid":"d3d2b84c050fb4d27625ffaf57471948766504df","tid":1896531,"uid":107297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T07:45:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9429593a72a61305c7e21098952e414b19fe1cc","tid":1896531,"uid":49336,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T07:48:40.000Z","msg":"但係泛民可唔可以唔好玩自爆，比<span style=\"color: red;\">黑材料</span>D五毛呢？<br />\n<br />\n黑材料係支那話 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你唔識用 證據 醜聞 痛腳 把柄 呢啲字？"},{"pid":"827abff1e7151b64bbd1fe1d310a9d482de76ab4","tid":1896531,"uid":107297,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"b9429593a72a61305c7e21098952e414b19fe1cc","tid":1896531,"uid":49336,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T07:48:40.000Z","msg":"但係泛民可唔可以唔好玩自爆，比<span style=\"color: red;\">黑材料</span>D五毛呢？<br />\n<br />\n黑材料係支那話 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你唔識用 證據 醜聞 痛腳 把柄 呢啲字？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T07:53:02.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20161122/55948543\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Freal